6|58|Say: 'If what you seek to hasten were with me, the matter between you and me would be decided; and God knows very well the evildoers.'
6|59|With Him are the keys of the Unseen; none knows them but He. He knows what is in land and sea; not a leaf falls, but He knows it. Not a grain in the earth's shadows, not a thing, fresh or withered, but it is in a Book Manifest.
