30|58|Indeed, We have struck for the people in this Koran every manner of similitude; and if thou bringest them a sign, those who are unbelievers will certainly say, 'You do nothing but follow falsehood.'
30|59|Even so God seals the hearts of those that know not.
30|60|So be thou patient; surely God's promise is true; and let not those who have not sure faith make thee unsteady.
31|1|Alif Lam Mim
31|2|Those are the signs of the Wise Book
31|3|for a guidance and a mercy to the good-doers
